release_note: Welcome to our biggest update ever! We ve been working incredibly hard behind the scenes and have rewritten 80 of our codebase to bring you a seamless bug free experience. Here s what you can expect from our latest release: Introducing My Paths: Navigate to the new My Paths section for specialized learning opportunities. We re kickstarting this feature with an anxiety course aimed to provide personalized help and guidance to all our users. Revamped Screen Time Section: We ve rebuilt this area from the ground up. Discover an improved way to track your use all paired with a better onboarding process to enable a smooth start. Scheduling Functionality: Maintain discipline and achieve better screen time habits with our new app blocking schedule. Define time frames to lock specific apps and create a distraction free environment to focus better. Emotional Trends Analysis: In our constant effort to promote mental well being we ve introduced emotional trends analysis. Understand your mood patterns better and use the insights for a smoother life journey. Redesigned Today Screen: Your Today screen now comes with fresh daily exercises related to the path you re following. Practice self therapy with a new exercise each day. Bug Fixes: We ve taken your feedback to heart and squashed a lot of bugs to enhance the stability and performance of the app. We ve got more thrilling updates on the way! Thank you for continuing to be a part of our journey. Don t forget to stay tuned for up and coming features as we continue refining and expanding our app to enhance your experience.
Introducing our new light theme! We ve also fixed some bugs and made small improvements.

We re excited to announce a new feature that allows you to schedule app blocking on your phone. Whether you want to block social media in the morning or evening this new feature gives you the power to control when and how you use your apps. This is a great way to help you focus on what s important and we can t wait to hear how you use it!
This update brings a bunch of small improvements and fixes. We ve also added a number of reasons for your emotional state. Just check in!
The new Apple Watch app is here! Track your emotional state on the go and get real time feedback. We ve also squashed some bugs and made some improvements.

This update contains both internal and user facing improvements: You can now replay and share a session from the History screen. A sensitive data disclaimer is now displayed for Open Ended Questions in materials. All your answers are stored on your device locally and we do not have access to them. We are committed to protecting your privacy! The Settings menu now includes an Information section. Here you will find the link to our official Discord channel. Feel free to join us and share your thoughts!
